{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0be6194778","title":"“反右杂感”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"127184f04b","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"0be6194778"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"133dac295f","name":"李文咸"},{"id":"f46655e252","name":"湖北"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2ca69f2765","type":"title","text":"“反右杂感”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"684eede2dd","type":"authors","text":"湖北李文咸","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"b8bad4fc35","type":"subtitle","text":"（李文咸：湖北省合作干校教学工作人员）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"4ec7394f62","type":"paragraph","text":"他们都是在反右的名义下，各自打算着自己的如意算盘：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"60097a1471","type":"paragraph","text":"有的是借运动泄个人私愤，","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"4119e8efcb","type":"paragraph","text":"有的想在斗争中一举成名(入党)，","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"4e2704e16f","type":"paragraph","text":"有的为了是向领导大献殷情，","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"4f5b959b1e","type":"paragraph","text":"有的是为了晋级职位又高升。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"992d4cb125","type":"paragraph","text":"他们有的是为了将功赎罪，","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"2105ac7603","type":"paragraph","text":"也有的是为了苟且偷生，","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"9d788c2bbd","type":"paragraph","text":"也有的是为了表示自己对组织的忠诚，","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"d0e3bffe4a","type":"paragraph","text":"又有人是为了解除领导上对自己的不满。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"e483c2246a","type":"paragraph","text":"他们都各有各的美梦来参加这一伟大的运动！","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"28dbdb5518","type":"paragraph","text":"斗争！","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"35b3d01072","type":"paragraph","text":"*  　*　　*","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"1482ae00a1","type":"paragraph","text":"这场戏我看得差不多了，我应该归去！","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"62974a0dd6","type":"paragraph","text":"吾名已受辱……","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"2adf04676f","type":"appellation","text":"……","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"fb7cc9f120","type":"paragraph","text":"我很骄傲归去，因为我为大家争取了民主，","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"363032eb2d","type":"paragraph","text":"没有胡风在文艺上放一炮！不会有百花齐放百家争鸣的提出。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"3223d7161d","type":"paragraph","text":"没有我们在民主问题狠狠放一炮！大家是不会取得很好的民主生活。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"678d01a7e5","type":"paragraph","text":"我是以一个纯洁之身来到这个人间，","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"d3169cfbbf","type":"paragraph","text":"我将以一个清白之身与这个美好的人间脱离，","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"877667584b","type":"paragraph","text":"如果说我在这个世界上有点什么痕迹的话，","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"e85180326e","type":"paragraph","text":"那就是我曾经也作过共青团员。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"1f3582ffe8","type":"paragraph","text":"沧浪之水清兮，","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"d660188614","type":"paragraph","text":"可以濯我头巾，","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"fdfb45b6a2","type":"paragraph","text":"沧浪之水浊兮，","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"da60021ddf","type":"paragraph","text":"可以洗吾泥足。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"},{"id":"54a14ae1a0","type":"appellation","text":"来源：《右派言论选集(续编)》（中共湖北省委宣传部编，湖北人民出版社，1958）。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778"}],"page":{"id":"9e9f336e27","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0be6194778","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}